charphrases: Sorry, but I’m a bit busy right now. I’m trying to enjoy my coffee and would also enjoy the personal space.
I am having a (come up with a really really extravagant drink with too many toppings lol). I highly recommend it.
I would go get another drink and a pastry but my seat is too comfortable. Since you already went out of your way to talk to me, can you go grab me some more?
Great! I’ll keep staring at the crumbs in the meantime. Don’t forget, I want a (BLAH BLAH BLAH) and a slice of bread.
Don’t they look so delicious?! It’s hard to pick which one! Or maybe I should get all of them…
